  "subject": "[DCAEGEN2] Datalake 1.1.3 images",
  "commit_message": "[DCAEGEN2] Datalake 1.1.3 images\n\n- update datalake related images (1.1.1 -> 1.1.3)\n- adjust kafka config to advertise FQDN broker addresses [0]\n\n[0] this resolves an issue in SO in which the SO cannot find the broker\n    because the dns resolver cannot find it\n\nIssue-ID: DCAEGEN2-3435\nChange-Id: I8cc306d189b3b0a6230b4c14f41b0e0a3a15c40a\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
